<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Palika GIS Demo Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        @keyframes gradientAnimation {
            0% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }
            50% {
                background-position: 100% 50%;
            }
            100% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }
        }
        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 10px auto;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f9fafb 100%);
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(50, 50, 93, 0.1), 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: slideIn 0.7s ease-out;
        }
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(
                -45deg, 
                #4a90e2, #50c878, #4a90e2, #50c878
            );
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            animation: gradientAnimation 10s ease infinite;
        }
        .email-header h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .email-header h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: white;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 10px 15px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .email-body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4a90e2, #50c878);
        }
        .email-body p {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            color: #34495e;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .credentials-table {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        .credentials-table tr {
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .credentials-table tr:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        }
        .credentials-table tr td {
            padding: 4px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .credentials-table tr td:first-child {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4a5568;
            width: 40%;
        }
        .validity-notice {
            background-color: #e6f4ea;
            border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #2e7d32;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .email-footer p {
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .email-footer a {
            color: #4a90e2;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .email-footer a:hover {
            color: #50c878;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h2>Palika GIS Demo Booking Confirmation</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= firstName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for booking a demo of Palika GIS. We're excited to introduce you to our platform.</p>
            <p> Visit: <a href ="https://www.palikagis.com">www.palikagis.com</a> and try out our demo.</p>
            <p>Below are your login details:</p>
            
            <div class="credentials-table">
                <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; word-break: break-all;">
                    <tr>
                        <td>User Name:</td>
                        <td><%= receiverMail %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Password:</td>
                        <td><%= password %></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <div class="validity-notice">
                Your login credentials will be valid till <%= validity %>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you encounter any issues or have questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
            <p>We look forward to having you on board and helping you explore the power of Palika GIS!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><strong>Palika GIS Team</strong></p>
            <p><a href="mailto:support@palikagis.com">support@palikagis.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>